event.title: FSFE at T-DOSE 2025 in Eindhoven, Netherlands

body.p: Lucas Lasota, FSFE programme manager, will be at T-DOSE 2025 in Eindhoven (The Netherlands) on May 31 and June 1. On May 31, from 15:00 to 15:50 (CEST), he will give a talk about "Shaping the future of the Internet with Free Software," entangling FSFE's work on device neutrality and Free Software and AI and presenting the Next Generation Internet initiative.
